      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in great shape, having been well-maintained and cared for over the years. It drives smoothly and looks wonderful, showing only the minor, honest signs of use you'd expect from a vehicle that's been loved but kept in solid condition. It\u2019s a reliable, high-quality choice that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
