    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong finish, though upon closer inspection, you will notice some light surface scratches and a few minor stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only moderate wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
