    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very sound, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience with no current issues to report. The exterior remains attractive with a strong finish, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches from normal road use. The interior is clean, comfortable, and smoke-free, showing only slight wear on the upholstery. It is a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that is ready to drive immediately.",
