    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality unit, boasting an immaculate exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains in as-new condition. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, making this one of the finest examples currently available on the market. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this offering stands as a benchmark of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
