    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty in person. It is honestly in pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've absolutely pampered this car, and it's finally ready for its next home. If you're looking for a ride that's been meticulously cared for and kept in top-notch shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
