    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or imperfections, further protected by a recently applied professional-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is original, featuring factory-perfect gaps and an entirely clean front end free of stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery retains its original factory suppleness and scent, with absolutely no bolster wear, stitching pull, or UV-related fading. All interior electronics\u2014including the high-fidelity surround sound system and the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive maintenance log included. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
